{"TopicId":180318,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Make landing gear light to stop shine through wing parts","CreatedByName":"BadLeo","CreatedById":107972,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T16:11:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"BadLeo","CreatedById":107972,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T16:11:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDunno if I\u0027m alone on that one, but the lights of a retracted lading gear shining through and being visible on the other side of wing parts is one annoying glitch. Make it stop, maybe? Thanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tonka Crash","CreatedById":189552,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T22:42:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI put the lights\u00A0in the gear action group, so they come on as the gear extends and shut off on retraction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cavscout74","CreatedById":181783,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T22:46:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223499025\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543963374\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022189552\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tonka Crash\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Tonka Crash said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI put the lights\u00A0in the gear action group, so they come on as the gear extends and shut off on retraction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDitto.\u00A0\u00A0 Would be nice if they defaulted to that though\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BadLeo","CreatedById":107972,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-05T01:31:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223499025\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543963374\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022189552\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tonka Crash\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Tonka Crash said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI put the lights\u00A0in the gear action group, so they come on as the gear extends and shut off on retraction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI feel stupid to not have thought of that before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223499029\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543963610\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181783\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cavscout74\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Cavscout74 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDitto.\u00A0\u00A0 Would be nice if they defaulted to that though\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep, it feels it should be...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}